       <tr>
         <td>A1</td>
         <td>8</td>
         <td>Right shoulder round with neighbour</td>
       </tr>
       <tr>
         <td></td>
         <td>8</td>
         <td>Neighbors swing</td>
       </tr>
       <tr>
         <td>A2</td>
         <td>8</td>
         <td>Long lines forward and back</td>
       </tr>
       <tr>
         <td></td>
         <td>8</td>
         <td>1s swing, end facing up</td>
       </tr>
       <tr>
         <td>B1</td>
         <td>6</td>
         <td>1s circle left 3/4 with the dancer on their left</td>
       </tr>
       <tr>
         <td></td>
         <td>2</td>
         <td>1s make an arch and shoot that dancer across to their partner</td>
       </tr>
       <tr>
         <td></td>
         <td>8</td>
         <td>Partner swing</td>
       </tr>
       <tr>
         <td>B2</td>
         <td>12</td>
         <td>Circle left 1 1/4 (until everybody is facing direction of progression)</td>
       </tr>
       <tr>
         <td></td>
         <td>4</td>
         <td>Balance and Pass through along the line</td>
       </tr>
     </tbody>
   </table>
   <p><b>Note:</b> 1s are facing down the hall. 2s are facing up to the band.</p>
